name Pashto (Yusufzai)
language ps-x-yusufzai
language ps 5
maintainer Hanif Rahman <hanifkhan@gmail.com>
status testing

// Yusufzai (northern) Pashto realizes ښ as [x] and ږ as [ɡ], unlike the
// southern (Kandahari) retroflex fricatives [ʂ] and [ʐ] used by the base
// ps voice. The replace rules convert the shared dictionary post-lookup.
replace 00 S. x
replace 00 Z. g
